{"tid":999431,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恒地尚悅‧嶺加價2% 195呎最平327萬","createTime":"2019-01-28T16:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T23:10:56.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c98e5a0bbc9c702ff867531ef79bc528fd0b4c","tid":999431,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T16:37:45.000Z","msg":"四叔講得出做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n恒地(012)元朗尚悅‧嶺剛加推全新89伙，折實平均呎價16,174元，與去年10月首張價單的折實平均呎價15,881元比較，加幅不足2%。其中1座27樓J室開放式單位，實用面積195方呎，定價382.4萬元，呎價19,610元，扣除最高3%折扣後，折實價約371萬元，呎價19,022元創項目新高。入場單位為1座2樓J室開放式單位，實用面積195方呎，折實價約327萬元。"},{"pid":"fa723f56d3a71cccb2676d66807e70c39a98ed77","tid":999431,"uid":190540,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T16:45:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29564a99855aba29394bbd4bbca774b6d880c4fc","tid":999431,"uid":210161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T00:50:43.000Z","msg":"多人買咩 又偏僻又納米 <br />\n仲加價？"},{"pid":"856fd229e0345349e2220f39901ae2723f7c6aab","tid":999431,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:04:52.000Z","msg":"第一張價單清晒未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c796f0ac20e05876eea23522439286421554c7c","tid":999431,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"856fd229e0345349e2220f39901ae2723f7c6aab","tid":999431,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:04:52.000Z","msg":"第一張價單清晒未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"應該賣晒 而家第1座淨返六十零個單位 加推第2座價單<br />\n原來呢個月都靜靜雞賣左幾十個"},{"pid":"665fb4b4b0b639f3b2a04e90638bca95b292f4c8","tid":999431,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s